{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"LocalBusiness","name":"Southern Oklahoma Technology Center","image":"https://s3-media0.fl.yelpcdn.com/bphoto/MiiVMcetK7hR0VALOIprxQ/l.jpg","telephone":"(580) 223-2070","address":{"streetAddress":"2610 Sam Noble Pkwy","addressLocality":"Ardmore","addressCountry":"US","addressRegion":"OK","postalCode":"73401"},"review":[{"author":"Lynne T.","datePublished":"2019-08-01","reviewRating":{"ratingValue":5},"description":"Beautiful campus. 

Southern Tech staff encountered were professional and added to the overall success of our Employer focused seminar held in their conference center on 7.31.2019.  The auditorium well accommodated all registrants. Every Modern high-tech aspect one could ever want or need for that matter.  The conference center catered to our every request.  Presenters were able to move about freely with mobile sound mic kits--- so perfect.  Who likes to stand behind a podium for hours?? Noooo way! Nor were you required to do so. It is my experience that attendees are 100% more interactive and engaging when uninstructed. Auditorium Seating as expected, of course, with comfortable swivel chairs and tables for note taking. Very spacious conference space. 

By the way, the campus conference center building 200 is undergoing massive renovation but did not at all interrupt our meeting.  Sound was impeccable. Meeting was not impacted by construction noise."}],"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":5,"reviewCount":1}}

